## Additional Changes (latest amend)

- Per-bar colors from SERIES_PALETTE for categorical and horizontal bars
- PLAIN_FILLS (█, ▓, ▒, ░) for plain/no-color mode bar distinction
- Stacked time-series bars use fill chars in plain mode
- Color-keyed legend (■/fill markers) replaces letter keys (A:, B:, C:)
- Y-axis gutter width fix: considers widest of all 3 tick labels (max, mid, 0)
  to prevent bar overflow when mid-point label is wider (e.g., 3.5K vs 7K)
- Freed 1 footer line (no letter-keys row) → taller bars
